{% macro coverText(dueDate) %}
<div class="block">
  <div class="item">
    <p>Send us your return by <span class="bold">{{ dueDate | date }}</span>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <p>
    You must complete an abstraction return even if you have not abstracted any water (nil return).<br>
    If your licence has expired or been revoked complete the return up to the end date<br>
    of the licence.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <p>
    Before sending it make sure you:
    <ul>
      <li>have filled in all the relevant sections</li>
      <li>
        ticked the ‘nil return’ box if no water<br>
        has been abstracted
      </li>
      <li>signed the declaration</li>
    </ul>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <p>
    If you are required to carry out monitoring<br>
    as a condition of you abstracting water you need to continue sending this information<br>
    to your local area office.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="item">
    <p class="bold">Return the completed form to:</p>
    <p>
    Waste and Industry Regulatory Services<br>
    Environment Agency<br>
    Quadrant 2, 99 Parkway Avenue<br>
    Sheffield, S9 4WF
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

{% endmacro %}
